# Dachshunds: An Overview

Dachshunds, also known as **wiener dogs**, are a popular breed known for their long bodies and short legs.

## Characteristics of Dachshunds

Dachshunds are *incredibly* unique in their appearance and have a fascinating history. Plus they are very cute and tiny!

### Table: Dachshund Characteristics

| Trait          | Description               |
|----------------|---------------------------|
| Body Shape     | Hot dog shaped            |
| Coat Varieties | Smooth, Longhaired        |
| Temperament    | Playful, ferocuois, Brave |

#### Dachshund Image

![Dachshund](Dachhund.jpeg) 

#### Learn More

For more information about dachshunds, visit [American Kennel Club](https://www.akc.org/dog-breeds/dachshund/).
